, "likes": 586}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZCyzv96", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 87, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8533140, "raw_content": "", "author": "InDethWeTrust", "created": 1775216335604, "profile_picture": "CfKBb4de1sB6", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZCyzv96.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/nLe6DwAZA2xP.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/xH2PP78EeOiuV0Zz.jpeg", "width": 768, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 679}], "blurhash": "UDH27q?b~SRjO?S~H=IT$+IVE2t7IUNGs:NF", "full_resolution": [2146, 2429]}, "title": "The daily reminder . God bless Donald J Trump! ", "last_comment_created": 1775216335600, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 0, "score_up": 87, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZCz1IWZ", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 33, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "god", "id": 8533663, "raw_content": "It is indeed a Good Day, frens!\n\nThe only way to God the Father is through Jesus Christ, and through Jesus Christ, all things are possible! We were doomed, and needed a power greater than ourselves, the Lord, to take us out of sin and be born again and saved. \n\nIf it wasn't for JESUS himself, I would probably not be typing this right now. I was drinking over a liter of vodka (1,000-1,250ml or so) every single day for years. There was no chance of me stopping alone. Zero. I was at the point where I had to keep drinking 24/7, or I could have a seizure and die. Alcohol addiction is the devil and Jesus saved me from that. I was terrified of going to detox - but it was either that or death, and God gave me the strength to battle the FEAR of going through that. My body doesn't need alcohol anymore. I surely think of it everyday, and I'll never be able to control the drinking itself, but only through God can I find the strength to not pick up that first drink. And if God could get me through that absolute pit of hell, he can surely do anything. 73 days sober. \n\nThe love Jesus has for us infinite. Pray for his will, and it will be done. \n\nHave a blessed day everyone. \n\nMatthew 19:26", "author": "MedicallyReddit", "created": 1775235291357, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "MrTexan", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Good Friday - Christ died for us so that we shall not perish but be saved!", "last_comment_created": 1775237418534, "content": "<p>It is indeed a Good Day, frens!</p>\n<p>The only way to God the Father is through Jesus Christ, and through Jesus Christ, all things are possible! We were doomed, and needed a power greater than ourselves, the Lord, to take us out of sin and be born again and saved.</p>\n<p>If it wasn't for JESUS himself, I would probably not be typing this right now. I was drinking over a liter of vodka (1,000-1,250ml or so) every single day for years. There was no chance of me stopping alone. Zero. I was at the point where I had to keep drinking 24/7, or I could have a seizure and die. Alcohol addiction is the devil and Jesus saved me from that. I was terrified of going to detox - but it was either that or death, and God gave me the strength to battle the FEAR of going through that. My body doesn't need alcohol anymore. I surely think of it everyday, and I'll never be able to control the drinking itself, but only through God can I find the strength to not pick up that first drink. And if God could get me through that absolute pit of hell, he can surely do anything. 73 days sober.</p>\n<p>The love Jesus has for us infinite. Pray for his will, and it will be done.</p>\n<p>Have a blessed day everyone.</p>\n<p>Matthew 19:26</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 33, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "\u271d\ufe0f\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0UNDER GOD\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u271d\ufe0f", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2040029898295632377", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZCz0kMR", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 49, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8533457, "raw_content": "", "author": "Belleoffreedom", "created": 1775227495146, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "I_love_liberty_2", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZCz0kMR.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/DrJStrategy/status/2040029898295632377?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Trump's Timing", "last_comment_created": 1775237850427, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_t